Definition: the quality of having or showing the tenderness and warmth and affection of or befitting a mother
Example: the girl's motherliness made her invaluable in caring for the children
Synonyms: adj, all, maternal, motherly, maternalism, maternalistic, maternal_quality, maternity, parental_quality, the, quality, of, having, or, showing, tenderness, and, warmth, affection, befitting, a, mother, girl, s, made, her, invaluable, in, caring, for, children
Category: noun.attribute
